article_title: Family of missing Cassandra "Casey" Johnston refuses to give up search two weeks after she disappeared in Philadelphia
meta_description: Cassandra “Casey” Johnston, 26, was last seen leaving a friend’s house in Philadelphia at 5:51 a.m. on July 10, 2021. She was driving a silver 2016 Ford Focus with Pennsylvania license plate: KSA8807. The car was seen on security video on Franklin Street heading toward I-95 at 5:52 a.m. Her cell phone, which she had dropped earlier in the evening on her walk from the bar to her friend’s house, was located the next day by a city worker. She hasn’t been seen or heard from since. The Lower Southampton Township Police Department is investigating.
